description: Enticed Shaved Ice truck offers the Dallas / Fort Worth street vending, events, parties, and more.Once you try our products you'll notice an immediate difference. Our ice is freshly shaved off a block as they do in Hawaii, not from everyday cubed ice you normally get. The flavors will cause an immediate sensation in your taste buds and you'll be hooked. We take pride on our consistency as well as attention to detail, and look forward to sharing it with you. You’ll be able to tell we don’t take ourselves too seriously, just our products and customers. It's great to see the familiar faces as we serve all around the metroplex. Whether it's your first time or you are a loyal follower, we thank you for your support and hope to see you again!
name: Enticed Shaved Ice
